# Placeholder for the PRIMARY OTA bundle signing pubkey (D54).
#
# At build time, CI replaces this file's contents with the real minisign
# public key derived from MINISIGN_SECRET. The real pubkey lands in the
# baked image as /etc/agora/update-pubkey.pem. This .example file is
# committed only so that local builds outside CI have something present.
#
# DO NOT commit a real signing pubkey here — keep the build artifact
# canonical and the CI-substituted value the only source of truth.

-----BEGIN MINISIGN PUBLIC KEY (PRIMARY) — PLACEHOLDER -----
